author: ray_h
title: Go Kyung Pyo Will Melt Your Winter Hearts With Nylon Pictorial
text:
Go Kyung Pyo graced fans with a pictorial for fashion magazine Nylon Korea! 
The “ Don’t Dare to Dream (Jealousy Incarnate) ” actor went to Vienna, Austria for the photo shoot, posing in comfortable yet fashionable outfits perfect for the cold winter. 
While wandering around the beautiful city, Go Kyung Pyo’s boyish charms naturally came out, which complimented his street style with his own unique aura. 
After successfully finishing up “Don’t Dare to Dream (Jealousy Incarnate),” he won a New Star Award at the 2016 SAF Drama Awards. Let’s cheer him on and wish for his continued success throughout 2017! 
His pictorial is out now in the January edition of Nylon Korea. Check out more of the pictures below!
